OL,7,FThe four main teaching unions will
OL,8,Fcoordinate future strike action, in a
OL,9,Fmajor escalation of the ongoing
OL,10,Fteacher pay dispute that could spell
OL,11,Fchaos for schools in the autumn term.
OL,13,FAnnouncing the move in a joint press
OL,14,Fconference on Friday, the general
OL,15,Fsecretaries of the National Education
OL,16,FUnion (NEU), Association of School
OL,17,Fand College Leaders (ASCL), National
OL,18,FAssociation of Head Teachers (NAHT)
OL,19,Fand NASUWT said it marked an
OL,20,F"unprecedented show of unity".
OL,3,CThousands of schools face autumn
OL,4,Cclosure as all four unions pledge
OL,5,Csimultaneous strike action
